  "remainingGap": "The browser route now composes the seven generic-defense DSK aliases, but it still keeps minimal host convenience facades (`defenseFoundation`, `defenseBuild`, `defenseWaves`, and `defenseScale`) beside those DSK aliases so existing browser bridges keep working. Further local JavaScript shrink should replace convenience-facade calls with direct DSK semantic methods only after browser compatibility and descriptor consumption stay covered."
